As someone who has ingrown nails, i felt so much pain…
Never cut off your cuticles!  They protect your nailbed

ADVICE for treatment!! (I have done surgery 3 times, trust me!)
- If it bothers you a lot, see swelling, blood etc go to a professional one!! 
- DO NOT go to a general doctor, it needs more care than you think!
If it’s early stages:
- don’t cut your nails but treat them in straight line, not too deep.
- try to stand as less as possible.
- were comfortable shoes and socks. Not tight ones.
- Don’t try to put anything under your nail on your own cuz it may cause infections. Advice from my doctor since I used to do that…
